{"id":527285,"date":[{"year":1973,"month":4,"day":29}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"","column":"","genre":"","count":"532","ytitle":"","mtitle":"长大当个运动员(儿歌四首)","ftitle":"","authors":["张秋生"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们队伍长又长"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张秋生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿大街，过小巷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎朝霞，斗志昂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们练长跑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"队伍长又长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小鸟儿，唱起歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小树乐得鼓起掌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小鸟为啥唱?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——它夸我们干劲足，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"个个跑得热汗淌；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小树为啥乐?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——它看我们团结紧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"互相鼓励向前闯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一二一，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们每天都坚持，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"队伍越跑越是长……。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全家勤锻炼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天刚亮，起得早，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们全家往外跑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爷爷在打太极拳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爸爸妈妈做早操，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我和哥哥迈开步，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一二三四练长跑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为革命，勤锻炼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们全家记得牢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕天热太阳晒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕寒冬雪花飘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"练得身体棒又棒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工作学习有劲道。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长大当个运动员"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两张长凳一块板，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"门前搭张乒乓台，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大伙儿，围着看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们开展乒乓赛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小刚和小强，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打得真精彩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抽杀象流星，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"削球旋旋转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个进攻赛猛虎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个守球稳如山……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比赛完了拉拉手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大伙鼓掌齐称赞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夸他两人打得好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风格高来意志坚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小刚和小强，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"争着发了言:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我们互相来学习，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"友谊第一记心间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从小练得思想红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长大当个运动员。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小足球队"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小足球，圆溜溜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们都爱踢足球，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两块砖头做球门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哨子一吹就战斗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们小小足球队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踢起球来雄赳赳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"休息时，在一起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大伙忙个不停手——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"裤子破了自己缝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"足球坏了自己修，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你帮我，补球鞋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我给你，缝纽扣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"先进思想大发扬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艰苦朴素记心头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们小小足球队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命路上大步走。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入6号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1973\\04\\734t040301.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入6号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1973\\04\\734t040302.JPG\">"}]}